Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.65,JOJO4_textch,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:46.44,JOJO4_textch,NTP,0,0,0,,要被幹掉了 我吉良吉影要被幹掉了！
